2
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:05,250
But when I think of you

3
00:00:05,250 --> 00:00:06,598
My sweet child

4
00:00:07,744 --> 00:00:09,408
All I remember is your smile

5
00:00:10,816 --> 00:00:13,525
Watching the saurians ride the Spiritways

6
00:00:14,030 --> 00:00:17,375
 Or the feather from Uncle Chaco's hat dance in the wind

7
