One night, as you smiled up at the stars

8
00:00:22,592 --> 00:00:24,704
Your dad got lost in the sight as well

9
00:00:25,372 --> 00:00:29,376
Were you drawn in by some greater meaning, I wondered

10
00:00:30,625 --> 00:00:35,125
But, no. The stars were just smiling back

11
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,904
Aroni, stop writing, and join us!

12
00:00:40,450 --> 00:00:42,726
Team Leader, give us a toast!

13
00:00:43,825 --> 00:00:44,608
Okay, then...

14
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:49,792
May our homeland prosper, our friendship endure

15
00:00:49,792 --> 00:00:52,664
And may this be a journey we never forget!

16
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:56,450
Shh! He's laughing!

17
00:00:56,975 --> 00:01:00,032
I heard, babies that smile a lot are blessed with luck...

18
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:03,000
That's just superstition...

19
00:01:03,424 --> 00:01:04,475
It's true!

20
00:01:05,050 --> 00:01:06,402
None of us know the reason

21
00:01:06,402 --> 00:01:08,566
Behind all those smiles...

22
00:01:10,325 --> 00:01:15,081
But I think, you can sense all the love around you

23
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:16,375
Can't you?

24
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:18,895
We love you so much

25
00:01:19,575 --> 00:01:22,619
May you always be my happy boy

26
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:25,632
Where did these Abyssal monsters come from?

27
00:01:25,632 --> 00:01:26,528
Run!

28
00:01:27,225 --> 00:01:29,100
No good, exits are blocked!

