00:01:29,525 --> 00:01:30,616
Aroni, the babyâ€”

30
00:01:31,525 --> 00:01:32,322
Aroni!

31
00:01:36,525 --> 00:01:38,112
My child...

32
00:01:38,975 --> 00:01:41,675
Stay with me! I'm here! I'll protect you!

33
00:01:41,675 --> 00:01:45,175
Leave me... Just keep him... safe...

34
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:04,134
Gods, if you can hear my prayer...

35
00:02:05,758 --> 00:02:10,314
Take my body, my love, and my memories as fuel

36
00:02:11,325 --> 00:02:13,875
Even if my soul is barred from the Night Kingdom

37
00:02:14,497 --> 00:02:16,425
Doomed to wander the desolate wilds...

38
00:02:17,475 --> 00:02:19,662
I offer up all that I am...

39
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:23,714
...That this child might live

40
00:02:35,932 --> 00:02:40,028
I have no doubt, you'll meet many good friends one day

41
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,944
Because I know

42
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:45,574
You're the luckiest child there is

43
00:02:47,717 --> 00:02:49,367
Smile for me, my darling...

44
00:02:50,176 --> 00:02:53,760
Let Mommy see it... one last time

